  <item>
    <title>Vietnam ISPs</title>
    <link>http://www.saigonist.com/content/vietnam-isps</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;With the recent instability in Facebook access and some people reporting it blocked on one ISP or area of Vietnam while others can access it just fine... Is it time for you to rethink your choice in internet service provider?&lt;/p&gt;
